<br>
::Starting very quietly:: &quot;I have heard enough!&quot;<br>
::Now very loud:: &quot;HOW DARE YOU!?!&quot;  ::Looking about the room::<br>
<br>
&quot;Have you ALL forgotten where you are?  This is a Temple of Poseidon.  You DO NOT walk in here and disrespect my brother the way ALL of you have.  Do I agree with that which my brother has done? No.  But the issue has grown beyond that!&quot;<br>
<br>
::He walks right up to Artemis, staring her dead in the eyes with his glowing Purple hues::  <br>
&quot;If you had qualms with Poseidon, You call him up to Olympus.  On Neutral ground for us all.  Yell and scream at him all you want up there.  Not here!  For one thing, prying mortal ears.  Secondly, and more importantly, this is HIS sanctum, his domain.  You do not walk into someone's home and dispresect them!&quot;<br>
<br>
::He walks up to Hera now and stares her in the eyes:: <br>
&quot;I hope you heard that which I spoke to Artemis, because I dislike repeating myself.  You of All should have known better, oh Sister.&quot;<br>
<br>
::He now turns his attention to Dawnitha, his eyes glow a bit deeper now:: Next time you walk into a god's Temple, you show them the proper respect!  You don't have to worship him, but you show him the proper respect within his own Temple.  I should strike you dead for your insolence!&quot;<br>
<br>
::His gaze now turned to the three Furies:: &quot;And since when was compassion part of your repitoir?  From what I understood you three were into torturing of souls, not in the prtoection racket.&quot;<br>
<br>
::He then turnes his back and continued pacing around the room.  He then turned to face the entire room once again::  <br>
<br>
&quot;Again, do I necessarily agree with what Poseidon has done? No.  Do the Amazons need to worship any god other than the ones they choose to?  No.  But I do expect them at least not to disrespect me or any other god or goddess for that matter!  Poseidon may have overstepped his bounds.  But so have all of you this day!  You have greatly disrespected my brother!&quot;  <br>
<br>
::His finger motions all around the room on this last sentence.  Having now said his piece, he begins walking back to the rift, very slowly, and still very methodically angry:: <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uixlordhadesxi.showPublicProfile?language=EN>IX Lord Hades XI</A> at: 6/5/01 3:24:05 am<br></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#FFFF33>- </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite>Amazons Unite</a><font color=#FFFF33> - </font><a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23>The Olympian Gods</a> <font color=#FFFF33> - </font><a href="http://www.amazonsunite.i-p.com">Home</a><font color=#FFFF33> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 6.3 b4<br>Copyright ©1999-2001 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  